i- Refer to		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
hDN42 Wiki's Bird1 Guide	URL:https://wiki.dn42.us/howto/Bird	{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i, where
a copy-paste-able config is available.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- You can directly use BIRD's official repo in Debian:		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- You may refer to		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
hBIRD's download page	URL:https://bird.network.cz/?download&tdir=debian/	{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
